{"type": "article", "id": 27638, "title": "Chanel 北京办秀，以及，Gentle Monster 纽约变身海底世界｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-01T11:55:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 28454, "name": "婚戒"}, {"id": 14026, "name": "度假系列"}, {"id": 15755, "name": "走秀"}, {"id": 31, "name": "英国"}, {"id": 3758, "name": "北京"}, {"id": 8238, "name": "墨镜"}, {"id": 341, "name": "运动"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 6474, "name": "联名"}, {"id": 7721, "name": "滑板"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 16355, "name": "Acne"}, {"id": 2684, "name": "Mansur Gavriel"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 28455, "name": "Palace"}, {"id": 28456, "name": "Bella Hadid"}, {"id": 19144, "name": "Kristen Stewart"}, {"id": 2175, "name": "李宇春"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021427225pFjyvxsmGX62Sbw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/chanel-takes-paris-rome-show-beijing-10440491/\"><b>Chanel 在北京办秀</b></a>｜昨日（5 月 31 日），Chanel 在北京举办了“巴黎在罗马”高级手工坊系列发布，Kristen Stewart、李宇春、陈伟霆、周迅、宋慧乔、窦靖童、杜鹃等艺人出席。这是香奈儿近十年来首次在北京办秀，吸引到超过一千名观众。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142647uXFc7hHlpV2igRUD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021426494hZBGHS03Y5P9XQt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142651MqcTpadwvBsiQKF1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021426525wcjLsUN7vlJCGfm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/05/hari-nef-mansur-gavriel\">Mansur Gavriel 首次找了知名模特拍广告</a></b>｜这两年以“水桶包”等大火的纽约品牌 Mansur Gavriel ，此前拍摄广告海报都采用模特不露脸的形式。最近品牌首次挑选了“熟脸”大牌模特 Hari Nef 为其拍摄广告，后者曾为 Gucci、Hood by Air 及 H&amp;M 这样的品牌走秀、拍摄海报。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142652I9Cemb5ahoKk6v4r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67419355\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/H-M-and-Bloglovin-launch-second-blogger-mentorship-program,694337.html#.V05A8oQrJQY\"><b>H&amp;M 与 Bloglovin 合作推出导师计划</b></a>｜H&amp;M 再次与 Bloglovin 合作推出“博主”导师制项目，博主们受邀参加这一比赛，获胜者可以得到网站 Man Repeller 的负责人 Leandra Medine 指导，以及前往 H&amp;M 纽约总部的旅行。 5 名获胜者得到 Medine 一对一的指导课程，九月还将公布冠军选手。</p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Bella-Hadid-becomes-makeup-ambassador-for-Dior,698434.html\">Bella Hadid 成为 Dior 美妆代言人</a></b>｜近日美国模特 Bella Hadid 与法国 Dior 美妆签约，成为品牌大使，将为 Dior 拍摄一系列在线视频，首发于 6 月 6 日。并且刚刚为 Dior 2017 早春度假系列走秀。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/dior-cruise-show-10440493/\"><b>Dior 举办早春度假大秀</b></a>｜周二，Dior 早春度假系列秀场在英国布莱尼姆宫（Blenheim Palace），后者是英国最大的建筑之一，建于 1700 年代早期，过去 Dior 曾在此地办过两次时装秀。这是 Raf Simons 离任后的 Dior 首场秀，由 Lucie Meier 和 Serge Ruffieux 带领的设计团队完成，狩猎印花、刺绣和天鹅绒等元素大量出现。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142653U8nfE1qmDr7u2zIZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142653TyG9jJYr2054EVzi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142654C4Zazi9GLQHmBY5l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021426557MtYUXHRmS3Fb2gC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142656ox3XtfVA15j9OJ8v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/palace-adidas-originals-2016-spring-summer-collection-part-2\">Palace 与 adidas Originals 发布联名春夏系列第二波</a>，6 月 4 日上市，包括复古感十足的田径运动服、轻薄 T 恤、帽子等单品：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142657hdutRUZzEk1rApgM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142657xHhUuFIn9mDE7RYq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142658oHN8ZnaGmMAy941O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142658SDPo3vkZ7zYtp8dC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142659L3pY4ymb8ZEBFeAV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142700ShU1XnbDWBmqK7gk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/resort-2017/paris/acne/review/\">Acne Studios 发布 2017 度假系列</a>，增添了更多色彩：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142701FgrWV9M7Li0mInuY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142702uv2LBrjEkZempswq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142703QkvWVs3eM9Y7ZhNJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142705joKIvWryPz8QkmcJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142705XnorBOwHifsbz4IU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">韩国墨镜品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/gentle-monster-grand-blue-installation\">Gentle Monster 近日将纽约旗舰店改头换面</a>，以电影《碧海蓝天》为灵感，设计了一个海底世界，这一主题将持续到 8 月 31 日：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142707xU1KqEPkhemuRcvM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142707mJKRG1S3YcUwjrhT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142708lstB4d8AMH5b6yEa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142709ntNl1EUWGcqO6Kge.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142710ls2bDWBgz1i4y0n3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142711NSf1VlRYZnHW5Osu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">老佛爷 <a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/13440966/weddings-karl-lagerfeld-engagement-rings/?mbid=social_facebook\">Karl Lagerfeld 设计了首个婚戒系列</a>，与珠宝品牌 Frederick Goldman 合作，为自己的同名个人品牌推出了四款婚戒，价格在 1000-10000 美元之间。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142711IhtsSpRqzDwJloH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50622407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142712yRXvGhZCnojWAtIb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50361197\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"> Supreme 与 ANTIHERO 继 2014 年的合作后，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/supreme-x-antihero-2016-summer-collection\">再次推出夏季联名系列</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021427149myQi3Dv5sXugePj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142714LcjTBp4HYJlmVh0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142715UYLsv34Fm5WxlbQq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142715LRXuKcyAi3IZ5SDT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142716m49BxqjUo6FvV3AG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021427163JfQ5gdLecK8wqnP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142717CFP2KUoOuS3hRY8L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142718vBYbsqpGKNjOFwnM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142718zOZpFkwldKI6iqh3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/5/31/11818424/shop-vans-x-other-stories-new-sneaker-collab\">Vans 与瑞典品牌 &amp; Other Stories 的联名款球鞋</a>来了，售价为 100 美元：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021427198mnXTI6HwstZipga.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021427191aEo3CKu8vwzf0Vl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142720p28gYzBWnsGqVXjE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142720BvmjdiCu47EGzPe9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}